OIN THE COMMUNITY</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Create private races  with your friend or join other sailors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Join the community in VR, on Discord </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">MarineVerse Sailing Club is developed by a small dedicated indie team based in Australia, whose mission is to inspire, train and connect sailors.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join us now and be part of the journey!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(*) Extra features unlocked with monthly <strong>Sailing Pass</strong> - available for $13/month.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Finish race","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/1878daf0ac79c0fd451647f676a77d1912da3a5c.jpg"},{"name":"Sailing Terms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/f44506f5680c025da8ba060245a325f148022bd3.jpg"},{"name":"Finish race in a Dinghy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/104fc81a1bb1af29332a4395bb24a3fa1748c7ce.jpg"},{"name":"Finish tutorial","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/7955e42f00a7ca666ad14115dd1d416b99f0beba.jpg"},{"name":"San Francisco","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/b0a784f1aad3ddf737699b0dc5b037b19d57e5d3.jpg"},{"name":"Seattle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/90e1aa1aba7af2d69aff77ad8ea8d24602ae9b47.jpg"},{"name":"Sydney","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/e23a7c5f03233832dd72b03d39c685ccac7007c4.jpg"},{"name":"Rules","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1035320/b80b03876a4830d0cd17fb109c6212d7031d7589.jpg"},{"name":" Sheet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/s